다음 SQL 쿼리의 결과로 올바른 것은 무엇인가요?

users 테이블: id(1,2,3), name('Alice','Bob','Charlie'), age(25,30,25)

SELECT age, COUNT(*) as count FROM users GROUP BY age HAVING count > 1;

